今週敵を倒したって？
defeated an enemy this week?

54
00:05:29,108 --> 00:05:31,408
って何回言えば分かるんだ
How many times do I have to say it for you to understand?

55
00:05:31,508 --> 00:05:34,408
僕は単行本派なんだ！
I'm a volume reader!

56
00:05:34,508 --> 00:05:38,208
ああ 次が出るのいつだっけ
Ah, when is the next volume coming out again?

57
00:05:38,308 --> 00:05:41,808
それ読むまでは絶対許さない！
Until I read that, I'll never forgive you!

58
00:05:52,708 --> 00:05:54,608
いつか僕らは
